<title type="html"><![CDATA[Research, Strats &amp; Routing • Re: Lobby Movement Time Chart]]></title>

<category term="Research, Strats &amp; Routing" scheme="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewforum.php?f=17" label="Research, Strats &amp; Routing"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=375&amp;p=2741#p2741"><![CDATA[
Fucked around with the CCM late route (standard 1st basement, of SSL/HMC/LLL then vanish) to see the best lobby order. Guess what, the route everyone has been using is the fastest one (lelelel). But don't even think about doing Dark World early.<br />Calculated the total lobby movement time for every single combination of the 3 levels + dw, using the numbers of my chart. Then used a little formula of mine to get the optimal slide points. (BOB is never the first stage bcos wingcap).<br /><br />The final line of each paragraph is the actual level order. All of them start with BOB(1), ending going to the basement.<br /><br /><br />~ ~ ~ ~ ~ Route (C) WF,JRB,BOB<br />~ ~ ~ ~ ~ CCM in between basements = +5.104<br />~ ~ ~ ~ ~ CCM before up = +7.140<br /><br />WF-DW-JRB-BOB 16884<br />+ JRB-S-BOB 0.633<br />+ WF-S-DW 1.068<br />WF-S-DW-JRB-S-BOB = 18.585<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #BF0000">WF-JRB-DW-BOB 12079<br />+ JRB-S-DW 0.367<br />+ -S-WF 2.670<br />S-WF-JRB-S-DW-BOB = 15.116<br /><br />WF-JRB-BOB-DW <br />+ JRB-S-BOB 0.633<br />+ -S-WF 2.670<br />S-WF-JRB-S-BOB-DW = 15.281</span></span><br /><br />WF-DW-BOB-JRB 14981<br />+ WF-S-DW 1.068<br />+ BOB-S-JRB 1.469<br />WF-S-DW-BOB-S-JRB = 17.518<br /><br />WF-BOB-DW-JRB 14581<br />+ WF-S-BOB 1.067<br />+ DW-S-JRB 1.502<br />WF-S-BOB-DW-S-JRB = 17.150<br /><br />WF-BOB-JRB-DW 17117<br />+ JRB-S-DW 0.367<br />+ WF-S-BOB 1.067<br />WF-S-BOB-JRB-S-DW = 18.551<br /><br />JRB-DW-WF-BOB 17318<br />+ JRB-S-DW 0.367<br />+ WF-S-BOB 1.067<br />JRB-S-DW-WF-S-BOB = 18.752<br /><br />JRB-DW-BOB-WF 14448<br />+ JRB-S-DW 0.367<br />+ -S-JRB 1.469<br />S-JRB-S-DW-BOB-WF = 16.284<br /><br /><span style="color: #BF0000"><span style="font-weight: bold">JRB-WF-DW-BOB 12613<br />+ WF-S-DW 1.068<br />+ -S-JRB 1.469<br />S-JRB-WF-S-DW-BOB = 15.150<br /><br />JRB-WF-BOB-DW 12779<br />+ WF-S-BOB 1.067<br />+ -S-JRB 1.469<br />S-JRB-WF-S-BOB-DW = 15.315</span></span><br /><br />JRB-BOB-DW-WF 13948<br />+ JRB-S-BOB 0.633<br />+ -S-JRB 1.469<br />S-JRB-S-BOB-DW-WF = 16.050<br /><br />JRB-BOB-WF-DW 17450<br />+ JRB-S-BOB 0.633<br />+ WF-S-DW 1.068<br />JRB-S-BOB-WF-S-DW = 19.151<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1469">SpectreXS</a> — 04 Dec 2014, 07:10</p><hr />
]]></content>
